org.apache.hadoop.fs.viewfs

Class TestViewFileSystemDelegationTokenSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.viewfs.TestViewFileSystemDelegationTokenSupport

  • public class TestViewFileSystemDelegationTokenSupport
extends Object
    Test ViewFileSystem's support for having delegation tokens fetched and cached for the file system. Currently this class just ensures that getCanonicalServiceName() always returns null for ViewFileSystem instances.
